    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Lernanthropus seriolii Shishido, 1898, adult ♀. A, urosome, dorsal view showing paired fifth legs, genital open- ings and caudal rami. Mitrapus oblongus (Pillai, 1964) ♂, B, habitus, dorsal. Scale bars A, 0.5 mm, B, 200 μm." ;
